The paper deals with understanding the content of images and videos, which is a core problem in computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing (NLP) to analyze the text in advertisements, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for classification tasks, which is a common theme in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG).
